Riki -- High-DPS, starting stats 4 int, 12 agi, 4 str, base speed 280, base damage 4, Stats Gain per level 0.40 int, 0.40 str, 0.60 agi
starting item Weak Dagger increase damage by 2 and give 3 attackspeed base attack time 1.40

LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1

5 armor 70 movement and 200 life

talent 2

8 base damage 20 attackspeed and 240 cast range



PASSIVE F OR D Thief Soul
increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF riki will gain 3 life per agility point he also gets 50% increase agility for a total of his intelligence and strenght he also got
a special dagger that cannot be change at all and he can use 1 more other dagger with it and he got 5% chance to evade any type of damage
DEBUFF riki only gain 2 life per strenght and he take 90% more damage from pure,magical,physical also he can only use dagger weapons type
he also lose 35% of his max mana with 20 attack speed lost and any pure damage type will do 2.5% of riki health as damage bonus

Roktoru Dagger Special
increase base damage by 2 increase by 1 for every 3 level
increase attack speed by 5 increase by 1 for every 2 level
Physical spell crit chance 10% increase by 1% for every 10 level
Physical spell crit damage 110% increase by 1% for every level
can also be use to deal 100% crit for a 1 time use with any spell of riki spell having 15% more crit damage as well
cooldown of 70 second

talent level 25 upgrade Thief Soul
add a new modifier Deadly
if riki attack the same target 3 time in a row the next attack will deal 2% of the target current life as damage and reduce their armor
by 1 that stack up to 10 this effect only deal 1% of boss current life and also make casting Dagger Strike and Blinks Strike on unit
below 40% life will take 45% increase damage from those spell


SPELL Q Dagger Strike -NOTE- all riki spell and passive will deal damage base on this total basic attack damage
deal damage and reducing the enemy damage and attack speed for a short duration and after dealing the damage, the dagger
will bounce up to 4 target doing less damage and also reducing damage but not attackspeed

Attack damage 140% 160% 180% 200% damage type physical
damage reduction 5% 10% 15% 20%
attack speed lost 10 15 20 25
bouncing dagger damage 70% 80% 90% 100% of attack damage
bouncing dagger damage reduction 3% 5% 7% 9%
debuff duration 7 second
mana cost 90 plus 2% of max mana
cooldown 15

talent level 10 upgrade Dagger Strike
increase damage by 50% -Note- 50% of this goes to the lesser damage bounce dagger
increase damage reduction by 10% -Note- 50% of this goes to the lesser damage bounce dagger
reduce mana cost by 40
reduce cooldown by 2

add a new modifier Poison Dagger
after striking the enemy,they will get poison dealing 6 plus 15% of agility pure damage per second and disabling regeneration
for 3, also increase the damage they take by riki spell by 20% and if their die under the effect of the poison, they will spread it
to other target for 50% increase damage and lasting 4 second instead and can also spread again


SPELL W Blink Stab
jump behind the enemy stunning them and dealing damage, after the stun the target get silence.

Attack damage 150% 190% 230% 270% damage type physical
stun 0.40 0.45 0.50 0.55
stun increase by 0.01 per agility point
silence 0.60 0.90 1.20 1.50
silence increase by 0.02 per agility point
mana cost 150 plus 1% of max mana
cooldown 28 26 24 22

talent level 10 upgrade Blink Stab
increase damage by 60%
increase stun by 0.15
increase silence by 0.30
reduce mana cost by 60

add a new modifier Stab Feast
after blinking on the target riki gets 30% increase damage and 15% of his damage become pure for 4 second, if any
enemy die by blink stab riki will get heal for 20% of his max health and increase the next blink stab damage by 15% this can chain
up to 60% more damage, this bonus is lost if the target doesnt die by blink stab


